description: Imagine Lithium Inc., a junior mineral exploration company, acquires, explores, and evaluates mineral properties in North America. Its flagship project is the 100% owned Jackpot Lithium property located in Thunder Bay, Ontario. The company was formerly known as Infinite Ore Corp. and changed its name to Imagine Lithium Inc. in February 2022. Imagine Lithium Inc. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
